info.name: DBS $oku Blacks Scythe
info.description: Goku Black, usually referred to as Black, is the main antagonist of the Future Trunks Saga of Dragon Ball Super. When it comes to his energy, it is pure darkness. But when it comes to his mind, he requires pure justice.
